<Plain
  title="Support · OpenAlarm"
  description="Get help with OpenAlarm: report bugs and request features on GitHub."
  heading="Support"
>
  <p>OpenAlarm is an alarm app for iPhone that makes sure you actually get up: alarms can require disarm challenges, check that you're still awake a few minutes after you stop them, and resist being silenced or force-closed.</p>

  <p>Found a bug or missing a feature? Open an issue at <a href="https://github.com/gretzke/open-alarm/issues">github.com/gretzke/open-alarm/issues</a>. That's where development happens.</p>

  <p>Prefer email? <a href="mailto:support@tryopenalarm.com">support@tryopenalarm.com</a></p>
</Plain>
